title: Shares of several basic materials companies are trading higher following strong US jobs data and continued optimism amid the reopening of the economy. These have lead hopes of an economic rebound and an increase in materials demand.

Shares of several basic materials companies are trading higher, potentially rebounding from this quarter's weakness.
